    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《异星狂奔》游戏软件是融合了平台跳跃和动作解密玩法的闯关型派对游戏，游戏支持1~4人本地及联机游戏。游戏将提供多种多样的关卡环境，包括上天下海的新奇冒险体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于演示版本</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演示版本涵盖了Boss战、城市主题关卡等精彩内容，支持本地及线上1-4人同时游玩。你可以邀请 Steam 好友联机，一同解锁更多关卡和任务，尽情享受游戏乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【勇敢队员向前冲】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演示版本提供四位属性各异、形象鲜明的角色，支持本地与在线 1-4 人同时畅玩。玩家能通过Steam好友邀请开启联机之旅，一同踏上愉快的冒险征程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/8bc98b25f6b2bcbb7f2293a6bf9bb863.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=446 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【牢记任务不落空】</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小队成员不光要突破莱姆星人占领区的机关陷阱，还必须在限定时间内完成总部要求的多个任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/e910eedd5a674d0226b621a2b12e879c.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【关关难过关关过】 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市，海洋，基地，宇宙，莱姆星五大环境，饱含海量个性满满，绝无重复的关卡设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/971e70c99785169b4bd48f6d73ad0277.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【轻松】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是个让你受苦的游戏，除了愉快的闯关玩法，你还将体验到：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >峰回路转的剧情故事 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精彩演绎的过场动画 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/82e75ccbefc81f48af7b02e4b8aed2e5.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/43979ddd0d2192d8c14ab13895a81cb2.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【BOSS挑战】 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心设计的BOSS战</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167250/extras/07ee9cf5fdcea753b97b48f367a01cfb.avif?t=1742307011\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >期待你能和家人或者朋友玩的愉快！欢迎大家把游戏加入到您的愿望单，可以关注我们社交平台账号，有最新的游戏进展，我们会在商店社区及社交平台上发布。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
